    "Identifikasi Otomatis": "Identifikasi Otomatis",
    "Requires University SSO login (email @kampus-non-merdeka.ac.id). Receives a subsidised fare (Rp3,000) and payment options using E-Toll Card or QRIS. Maximum of 4 seats per transaction.": "Membutuhkan login SSO Universitas (email @kampus-non-merdeka.ac.id). Mendapatkan tarif subsidi (Rp3.000) dan opsi pembayaran menggunakan Kartu E-Tol maupun QRIS. Maksimal pemesanan hingga 4 kursi per transaksi.",
    "Uses the Guest Access feature without login. Subject to a base fare (Rp5,000) to support bus operations. Payment must be via QRIS only (E-Toll is exclusively designed for Civitas ID Cards). Maximum of 1 seat per transaction.": "Menggunakan fitur Akses Tamu (Guest Access) tanpa login. Dikenakan tarif dasar (Rp5.000) untuk mendukung operasional bus. Pembayaran wajib melalui QRIS khusus (E-Tol didesain khusus ID Card Sivitas). Batas pemesanan dibatasi maksimum 1 kursi per transaksi.",
    "The system issues a single-use E-Ticket Barcode once the transaction is secured. Passengers must display a screenshot of the barcode on their app or phone when boarding the bus for authorisation by the officer.": "Sistem menerbitkan Barcode E-Ticket sekali pakai setelah transaksi diamankan. Penumpang diwajibkan menampilkan screenshot (tangkapan layar) barcode di aplikasi atau handphone saat menaiki palka bus agar diotorisasi oleh petugas.",
    "The smart system detects the user profile to differentiate order quota limits, payment method availability (E-Toll/QRIS), and integrated travel insurance limits.": "Sistem cerdas mendeteksi profil pengguna untuk membedakan batasan kuota pesanan, ketersediaan alat bayar (E-Tol/QRIS), dan limit asuransi perjalanan terpadu.",
    "Reservation Module Inclusion Update v3.0": "Pembaruan Inklusi Modul Reservasi v3.0",
    "The latest campus bus online messaging system update provides automated special seat management and automatic price subsidies to support an inclusive ecosystem.": "Pembaruan mutakhir sistem perpesanan daring Bus Kampus menyediakan manajemen autolock kursi khusus serta subsidi harga otomatis demi mendukung ekosistem inklusif.",
    "10-Second Absolute Lock Timer": "Timer Lock Absolut 10 Detik",
    "For passengers with disabilities, the front 4 seats will be computationally locked for a full 10 seconds from when the page is first rendered. The general public cannot occupy the seats while the countdown is running.": "Bagi penumpang dengan keterbatasan, 4 kursi terdepan akan dikunci secara komputasional selama 10 detik penuh sejak awal halaman dirender. Masyarakat umum tidak dapat menempati kursi selama batas hitung mundur berjalan.",
    "Released to the PUBLIC": "Pelepasan Untuk UMUM",
    "If 10 seconds pass and the seat is not taken by a disabled passenger, the UI animation will change the seat icon indicating a public transition. The seat is then freely available on a first-come first-served basis.": "Apabila 10 detik berlalu dan kursi tidak digunakan oleh penumpang disabilitas, maka animasi UI akan mengubah wujud ikon kursi menandakan transisi publik. Kursi tersebut bebas direbut secara *first-come first-serve*.",
    "Targeted Subsidy Policy": "Kebijakan Subsidi Tepat Sasaran",
    "When you activate the \"Priority Need Toggle\", the interface requires you to select an intensity level. For wheelchair users (High), the entire cost is fully covered (Free Rp 0) with a maximum claim of 1 priority seat per equity transaction. For the Pregnant/Elderly category, the fare returns to normal but front-zone access is freely open.": "Ketika Anda mengaktifkan \"Toggle Kebutuhan Prioritas\", antarmuka mengharuskan Anda memilih intensitas. Bagi pengguna kursi roda (Tinggi), seluruh biaya ditanggung penuh (Gratis Rp 0) dengan jatah klaim maksimal 1 kursi prioritas per transaksi keadilan. Sementara untuk kategori Ibu Hamil/Lansia, tarif dikembalikan normal namun akses zona depan terbuka bebas.",
    "Standing Area (Flexible Standing)": "Fasih Berdiri (Standing Area)",
    "The bus layout accommodates 16 main seats and 4 standing spots in the rear cabin sector (Capacity 17-20). This area automatically becomes an option whenever passenger flow peaks, without compromising boarding scanner comfort.": "Denah bus dirancang menampung 16 kursi utama dan 4 porsi berdiri pada sektor ekor kabin (Kapasitas 17–20). Area ini otomatis menjadi opsi sewaktu-waktu arus penumpang mengalami puncaknya, tanpa mengorbankan kenyamanan pemindai jalan naik.",
    "Moving Reservation Lock": "Penguncian Reservasi Bergerak",
    "If a fleet has transitioned to travel mode (Moving/Resting), the frontend system asynchronously disables the reservation button and instantly resets all booking simulations to prevent phantom queues.": "Bila suatu armada telah beralih status ke mode penjelajahan (Jalan/Istirahat), sistem frontend secara asinkron mematikan tombol reservasi serta mereset segala simulasi pemesanan secara instan guna mencegah antrean palsu.",
    "Cross-Continental Realtime Sensor": "Sensor Realtime Lintas Benua",
    "Utilises radar map instruments to block tickets for fleets that have already left the terminal.": "Memanfaatkan instrumen peta radar untuk memblokir tiket pada armada yang sudah meninggalkan terminal.",
    "Experiencing operational confusion or a critical technical issue?": "Mengalami kebingungan operasional atau kendala teknis krusial?",
